{"tid":696971,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"傳統針灸 vs 電針","createTime":"2018-06-10T14:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T03:06:03.000Z","uid":13738,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f67b75186585fc6c1c17ce9818a608cc2d08b2a","tid":696971,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"唔知大家buy邊套多啲呢<br />\n<br />\n傳統針灸：唔加電既針灸，只會取穴方式落針，之後做捻轉手法達至針感（酸、麻、脹或痛），針感持續時間長，刺激都較大<br />\n<br />\n電針：常見既針灸，落針就駁電，透過電流刺激達至針感，刺激時間短，刺激都可以因應電流大小而調節<br />\n<br />\n傳統針灸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電針 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5993fcb25bcd423aa4f3466facfbb321c56437","tid":696971,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"兩樣都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b186ad261b9eb332d20ffeba552c731976914f8","tid":696971,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5993fcb25bcd423aa4f3466facfbb321c56437","tid":696971,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"兩樣都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"傳統針灸刺激一定大好多嫁，唔加電只靠轉針，勁好多"},{"pid":"fe8bf2dd68c27681880c60d97674f1dba369006e","tid":696971,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b186ad261b9eb332d20ffeba552c731976914f8","tid":696971,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5993fcb25bcd423aa4f3466facfbb321c56437","tid":696971,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"兩樣都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"傳統針灸刺激一定大好多嫁，唔加電只靠轉針，勁好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"做完係會鬆左 ，但真係好痛好痛好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g